title: NASA and Imperial scientists detect epic meteoroid impact on Mars

media:group.media:title: NASA and Imperial scientists detect epic meteoroid impact on Mars
media:group.media:description:
NASA instruments co-developed at Imperial have detected a meteoroid impact on Mars that left a crater one and a half times the size of Trafalgar Square.
Credit: IMPERIAL COLLEGE LONDON, IPGP, CNES, JPL-CALTECH/NASA
